name: "Mear One: Live Art Experience" DVD
description: Official description Don't Blink! Live Art Experience is a kaleidoscope of images. Paintstrokes per minute vs. beats per minute. Quick cuts, brushstrokes blend with music. Colors light up the screen. The ambient soundtrack synergizes with the visuals to make a powerful phantasmagoria. Watch epic painting live start to finish. World famous Mear One conducts a clinic on the principles of painting. Live Art Experience is a dialogue between Mear One and visionary film maker Motion. Motion introduces a new appraoch to documenting art. 5 segments of avant garde filmmaking. Motion's cinematography mirror Mear One's prolific artistry. Shot & edited by Motion, witness Mear One rock canvasses all over Los Angeles. Night clubs, downtown cityscapes to Silverlake, the man paints down Babylon. Live art experience is original, unlike anything you've ever seen before. - Mear's art speaks for itself.. But watching this is an insight into his technique, speed, and mind. All of which you can't help but find impressive and intriguing!
